rpmlauncher.privacy.title: RPMLauncher Privacy Policy
rpmlauncher.privacy.content.1: To optimize the RPMLauncher user experience, the software will collect the following information
rpmlauncher.privacy.content.2:
- Operating system/version
- Software version information
- Software error information
- IP (Obfuscated)
- Page view information
rpmlauncher.privacy.content.3: The data collection services used by the Software are Google Analytics and SENTRY, and by using the Software, you agree to the privacy terms of these services.
